Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:24.77,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}待てよ！　邪悪な牙を剥いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:30.82,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}嗤う　悪のデスアーマー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:36.64,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺が！　俺たちが許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:42.50,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危険上等　ブレイブチェンジ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:48.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:24.77,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}住手吧！  剥下邪恶的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:30.82,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs22}嗤笑着  邪恶的Death Armour
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.00,0:00:36.64,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我不能！  我们不能原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.88,0:00:42.50,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}危险最高  Brave Change!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:48.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}超剑战队 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.37,0:00:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剑战队  Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城镇正在被袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的Death Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.84,0:00:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.90,0:00:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不可能赢的了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是最强的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可饶恕！Death Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要打倒你  让世界恢复和平！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:36.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第2话\NBlade Braver和便当
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.62,0:02:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？新部员？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  一年级的川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有剑道经验的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  换衣服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来测试一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.54,0:03:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊  把你卷入到奇怪的事情里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山啊  只要一有人入部首先就会去打倒对方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.80,0:03:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此来明示上下级关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.77,0:03:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女生也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  如果是女生他更会去欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山是个虐待狂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男女在一起活动的运动部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次男生都嚣张得无法无天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:27.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那些家伙都把社团活动\N当成正大光明显示自己力量绝佳的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  小珠！去打倒他  我们社团那个最大的坏人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给那个一直欺负我们的外山一点颜色看看！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:39.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…纪梨乃学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.76,0:03:44.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道服…没有其他的了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件已经是最小的了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…我太矮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面虽然可以折起来…但后面拖着会踩到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还是算了吧…回头等你把自己的拿来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  一定要比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有今天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷偷的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.27,0:04:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别回去啊  一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.73,0:04:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我教训了她就轮到你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是小学时候的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被高年级的学生给围住  打了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中的一个人拿起铁管乱挥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:43.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候  她出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个正义的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  就是小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的伙伴啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊  那么…开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山的竹刀可是碳素的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:20.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给打到可是很疼的哦  要是被击中前臂什么的简直就是下地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这家伙因为喜欢看对方痛苦的表情所以才使用碳素棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜哇  真差劲  真是恶劣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了  白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…川添同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意岩佐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不是正式比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太认真对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要知道这只是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般的剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的伙伴…英雄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西也不能当饭吃啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！面！面！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速度还挺快的  我都打不中啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.34,0:06:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认真来打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹有效！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.68,0:06:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:07:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道本身在得取一本的时候  要回到原地重整姿态才是应有礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不重整姿态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:08.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不说了么  又不是比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:10.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是看看你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.79,0:07:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  又不是拿到一本就算获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外山只是想打人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个虐待狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道的目的不是砍人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是通过学习剑术的道理  参悟武士的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非以打倒对方为目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.53,0:07:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了提升自己进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:43.40,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小珠  4岁）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  对你来说太早了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  希望你能了解  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑道是以礼开始以礼结束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最重视礼仪的运动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.24,0:08:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那时候起已经11年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也到了我不了解她的年龄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么晚了 她在学校发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.44,0:08:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  攻过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:26.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:30.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一般的剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.64,0:08:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:43.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:41.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样！根本不痛不痒！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太弱小了！这种攻击根本无效！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀…果然还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.64,0:09:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙裤太长  所以后面会踩住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  所以动作不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:22.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用力踩住  好危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.17,0:09:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.23,0:09:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腹！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  手滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:42.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样正好  外山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.49,0:09:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:51.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不方便后退
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.38,0:09:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就紧逼着上前打倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:58.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她好好明白比力气是赢不过男人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.87,0:10:01.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连汗都没有流…真不爽！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果靠我的力量  无论击中几次都是无效
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.64,0:10:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的刺击力道太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:20.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像要给坏人最后一击一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能使用刺击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是谁都不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年长的男人应该可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.68,0:10:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然仅限于学过剑道的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且要等你上高中后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这之前就封印起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:40.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学过剑道的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.79,0:11:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我成为…高中生了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.52,0:11:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦  回去吃碗拉面慢慢想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这种事情也很容易突然莫名其妙的就搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  外山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.53,0:11:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑倒了吗  你还真夸张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个不知道什么时候还会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候能与之抗衡的…就只有你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.57,0:12:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道能尽多少力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.11,0:12:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.87,0:12:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正义的伙伴  一年九班川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:13:02.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:13:02.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}超剑战队 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子火焰剑！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这样就结束了  Blade Braver！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管几次我都会复活的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么不管几次我都保护给你看！人们的笑容！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:18.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:19.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬  那个是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加入剑道部了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能提起干劲是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:34.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被朋友邀请去的吗？还是说听了老师建议？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.09,0:13:35.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了在坏人手中维护正义！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚发的复印件  下次交上来就行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.53,0:13:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.88,0:13:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.57,0:13:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭也没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.72,0:14:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不赶快搞定和前辈的比赛  小命都要不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要吃面包么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是中午剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我正在减肥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的！给我吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！好棒！面包面包！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.82,0:14:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下面包星人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下面包星人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.97,0:14:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锵～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是为了严格训练准备的大分量便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是只为段郎特制的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:31.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有男子气概呢  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家一起换着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.82,0:14:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我的梅干不能换着吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.89,0:14:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.10,0:14:49.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有一个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.16,0:14:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过米饭的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我就吃点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:06.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家是开杂货店的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  吃汉堡包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  小都都做的炸虾条也很美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我右手的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  感觉像是在被喂饲料…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.65,0:15:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠还很小  得多吃点长得大点才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开个玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会胖的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个二年级的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.08,0:15:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  她叫小鞘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我小中高一直一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她时常会这种的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下一句「好好等待吧  时间会解决一切」就不见人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年我们剑道部是怎么样的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成绩这方面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.18,0:16:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很普通  团体战能进二回战就不错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,个人的话偶尔男生会进半决赛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生一直都一般般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有指导者的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙很懒惰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  最近开始有干劲了我很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.24,0:16:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:30.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次初中时候怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.64,0:16:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好成绩是县八强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.82,0:16:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.07,0:16:43.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  一点都不厉害  没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.82,0:16:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么大不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.95,0:16:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连县大会都出场不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.57,0:16:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次都没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这类的就是废物了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:03.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…很厉害的  我很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:06.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大会这类呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.28,0:17:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有出场过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.99,0:17:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  真浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不出场也知道结果的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全国大赛优胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川添珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.82,0:17:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千叶纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宫崎都
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上桑原鞘子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.56,0:17:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还需要一个能成战力的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  首先得制作特训的计划了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.78,0:17:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有干劲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  吉川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.21,0:17:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么吵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你最近一直都没什么干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.37,0:17:58.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很让人担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.57,0:18:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近学生和老师都没有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  有点像笨蛋那样热血比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点热情过剩  只要能将学生指引到正确方向就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  就无法说出动机了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.28,0:18:24.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪梨乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说了打击要只靠手腕用力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～对不起  都成习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做个示范给她看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这才像真正的剑道部～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滴淌的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞舞的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潇洒的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.03,0:18:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你那是什么品味
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有示范了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肩膀放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.08,0:19:07.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  再示范一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次  段和小都都有在跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  在外面跑圈中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  小都都
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,段郎  要落后了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个家伙首先得从基础体力开始锻炼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.48,0:19:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…在附近的话感觉会很火大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:35.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  小都都可是要在练习比赛中出场的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点进行针对比赛的练习可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:40.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:43.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的实力还没有在实战中确认过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  认真的放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  不可以的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师怎么说也算是有自尊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:21.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能秒杀他的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  就算要赢也多少让他挥两下再赢嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连我也…生疏了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢剑道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师有干劲了  我也很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.69,0:20:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石田老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.97,0:20:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬  又收到了妈妈老家的特产
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.87,0:21:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  从我老家寄来了梅子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你最喜欢的  纪州有机梅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.42,0:21:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  爸爸  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要做成三明治分给大家
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我交到朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾乃光芒万丈不可违抗的Death Armor
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向你们正面传授三条死亡界的信条吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.08,0:23:59.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其一  不要有所好恶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.97,0:24:01.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其二  时刻要有反抗的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.99,0:24:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其三  即使是跟你很亲切的人也不要去相信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}　　　　 offence　　　 defence{\r}\N其四  要进攻首先要防御
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.89,0:24:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有四条  但是不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.52,0:24:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能够遵守好这四条的话\N你也能成为了不起的Death Boy了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿Death Metal用Deathice发挥Death的效果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.18,0:24:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的标题是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「BLACK和BLUE」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.88,0:24:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有上场  不看也没关系哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.98,0:24:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:19.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呜～
